snippet.title: Dreamy Duels ~ Tales of Heroes in Gensoukyo // Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/1477010/Dreamy_Duels__Tales_of_Heroes_in_Gensoukyo/

Dreamy Duels is a card game inspired by Touhou Project universe and various other classic card games. In this game, you can craft you own cards with card editor, and use them to engage other players in a diverse card game world.

Developed by 
IGensoukyo
